   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : Root Blazor router component for AbsenceApp V2.
                 Matches the current URL to a @page-decorated component and
                 renders it using the V2 BaseLayout shell.
                 Also acts as a lightweight auth guard: subscribes to
                 LocationChanged and redirects unauthenticated users to /login
                 whenever they navigate to any route other than /login.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-13  Initial implementation.
     - 2.0.0  2026-03-23  Switched DefaultLayout to MainLayout for V2 shell.
     - 2.1.0  2026-03-24  Verified for AbsenceAppV2; no functional changes.
     - 2.2.0  2026-03-25  Confirmed as V2 router after V1/V2 project split.
                          Removed ambiguity with V1; V1 router restored separately.
     - 2.3.0  2026-03-25  Fixed DefaultLayout from Layout.MainLayout (V1) to
                          Layout.MainLayoutV2 (incorrect namespace).
     - 2.4.0  2026-03-26  Corrected DefaultLayout to typeof(MainLayoutV2) and
                          added @using AbsenceApp.Client.Framework.Layout.
                          This resolves CS0234/CS0246 errors across all V2 pages.
     - 2.5.0  2026-03-26  Replaced typeof(MainLayoutV2) with typeof(BaseLayoutV2)
                          and updated @using to AbsenceApp.Client.Framework.Layouts.
                          MainLayoutV2 no longer exists; BaseLayoutV2 is the V2
                          authenticated-shell layout (CS0246 build error fix).
     - 2.6.0  2026-03-26  Phase 3 Layout Repair: injected NavigationManager and
                          AppStateService. Added OnInitialized and LocationChanged
                          handler that redirects unauthenticated users to /login
                          when they navigate to any route other than /login.
                          Implemented IDisposable to unsubscribe the handler.
     - 2.7.0  2026-03-29  Phase 3 & 4 completion: changed DefaultLayout from
                          typeof(BaseLayoutV2) to typeof(MainLayoutV2). New
                          routed pages that omit @layout will now default to the
